    <briefdescription>
<para>Structure containing the information of a part of the brain. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>It contains :<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>The number of neuron types that can be encountered in the part</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>the cumulative distribution of neurons in the neuron types</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>the probability of connection (for each type) to other parts of the brain.</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
<para>This structure depends on the brain to which it belongs. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
